data.description: Beautifully maintained ranch plan in exclusive Del Webb Traditions 55+ Active Adult neighborhood. Expansive gourmet kitchen with stylishly shaped island and all the countertop space the best cooks could ask for. 2 bedroom split plan with private, french door-office perfect for work-at-homers or quiet study. Enjoy sunrise and sunsets watching birds and wildlife from the screened porch and deck. Gorgeous cul-de-sac lot near walking trails, community pond, and community dog yard. Deck pre-piped for gas grill. Come see this amazing property in the highly sought after Traditions neighborhood. Minutes from old downtown Wake Forest boasting great shopping, dining, and craft breweries. Enjoy amazing Del Webb amenities including pool, fitness center, pickle ball courts, walking trails, and an expansive social calendar. One owner must be age 55 years or older.
